participant_1.name: Sophia
participant_1.personality: Determined, disciplined, and passionate about sports and healthy living.
participant_1.background: i am a gold medalist olympian. i love italian food and garlic bread. my favorite color is yellow. gymnastics is my favorite sport. i workout four hours a day.

participant_2.name: Larry
participant_2.personality: Creative, friendly, and nurturing with a love for cooking and baking.
participant_2.background: the county wide bake sale is where i feel most at home. i've a dogs. knitting is my passion. i love to bake cookies.
